  "epitaph": "Here lies the grill that never heated,\nThe C# scripts, half-completed.\nSixty-seven stars looked on in hope,\nBefore the scope lost all its scope.\nThe burger patty, raw and cold,\nA story left strictly untold.\nCommit at dawn, deleted by the eve\u2014\nRest in peace, `Git checkout -- .`.",
